data.description: Welcome to this lovely home located in the highly desirable North Phoenix Norterra Pointe subdivision. This single level home features 4 -bedrooms,1 office/bedroom, 2 baths. The open floor plan living area is seamlessly connected to eat-in-kitchen with ample cabinet space and pantry. Primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in-closet and ensuite bathroom. Low maintenance front and back desert landscaping, 2 car garage. This home offers easy access to the I-17 and 101. A few miles from Happy Valley Town Center surrounded with lot of shopping, dining, hiking trails, parks and A rated schools. Demand continues to rise in this area due to growth expansion and minutes away TSMC Semiconductor Chip Plant.
